text: <@U7SL518D6> I have been saying that since I met him.
Would anyone like access to the new site setting for setting a custom search results path?
<@U6GNQ7JBU> uploaded a file: <https://HubSpotdev.slack.com/files/U6GNQ7JBU/FA7F0DR0W/screen_shot_2018-04-13_at_2.15.16_pm.png|Screen Shot 2018-04-13 at 2.15.16 PM.png>
DM a portal if you want to test

Requests for `hs-search-results` will still render the search results page, so if you have extended the search modules this will NOT break any functionality but will require a slight HubL change to use `{{ site_settings.content_search_results_page_path }}`
